{"id": "art-117", "label": "Art. 117", "title": "Art. 117: Persoanele care au dreptul de a refuza să dea declaraţii în calitate de martor", "slug": "art-117", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 117: Persoanele care au dreptul de a refuza s&#259; dea\ndeclara&#355;ii în calitate de martor </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Au dreptul de a refuza s&#259; fie audiate în calitate de martor\nurm&#259;toarele persoane:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)<b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>so&#355;ul, ascenden&#355;ii &#351;i\ndescenden&#355;ii în linie direct&#259;, precum &#351;i fra&#355;ii &#351;i\nsurorile suspectului sau inculpatului;</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1304290191\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2561\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1304290191\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>*) Prin Decizia nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>175/2022</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, Curtea Constitu&#355;ional&#259; admite excep&#355;ia de\nneconstitu&#355;ionalitate &#351;i constat&#259; c&#259; solu&#355;ia\nlegislativ&#259; cuprins&#259; în art. 117 alin. (1) lit. a) din Codul de\nprocedur&#259; penal&#259;, care exclude de la dreptul de a refuza s&#259; fie\naudiate în calitate de martor persoanele care au stabilit rela&#355;ii\nasem&#259;n&#259;toare acelora dintre p&#259;rin&#355;i &#351;i copii, în cazul\nîn care convie&#355;uiesc cu suspectul sau inculpatul, este\nneconstitu&#355;ional&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)persoanele\ncare au avut calitatea de so&#355; al suspectului sau al inculpatului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_456115537\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2560\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_456115537\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)persoanele care au stabilit rela&#355;ii\nasem&#259;n&#259;toare acelora dintre so&#355;i sau acelora dintre\np&#259;rin&#355;i &#351;i copii, dac&#259; dovedesc c&#259; au convie&#355;uit\nsau convie&#355;uiesc cu suspectul sau inculpatul.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_80709973\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2559\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_80709973\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>*) Curtea Constitu&#355;ional&#259; admite excep&#355;ia de\nneconstitu&#355;ionalitate &#351;i constat&#259; c&#259; solu&#355;ia\nlegislativ&#259; cuprins&#259; în art. 117 alin. (1) lit. a) &#351;i lit. b),\ncare exclude de la dreptul de a refuza s&#259; fie audiate în calitate de\nmartor persoanele care au stabilit rela&#355;ii asem&#259;n&#259;toare acelora\ndintre so&#355;i, este neconstitu&#355;ional&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1876955402\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2558\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1876955402\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dup&#259; îndeplinirea dispozi&#355;iilor art. 119,\norganele judiciare comunic&#259; persoanelor prev&#259;zute la alin. (1)\ndreptul de a nu da declara&#355;ii în calitate de martor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2030495053\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2557\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2030495053\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; persoanele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) sunt de\nacord s&#259; dea declara&#355;ii, în privin&#355;a acestora sunt aplicabile\ndispozi&#355;iile art. 120 &#351;i 121.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2051234388\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2556\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2051234388\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Persoana care îndepline&#351;te una dintre\ncalit&#259;&#355;ile prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) în raport cu unul dintre\nsuspec&#355;i sau inculpa&#355;i este scutit&#259; de obliga&#355;ia de a\ndepune m&#259;rturie &#351;i împotriva celorlal&#355;i suspec&#355;i sau\ninculpa&#355;i, în cazul în care declara&#355;ia sa nu poate fi limitat&#259;\ndoar la ace&#351;tia din urm&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}